UI & Design rules:

- Stitch outputs are mid-fidelity only
- Do not treat Stitch as final design
- UI must be implementable in Tailwind

Visual language:
- Professional
- Trustworthy
- Calm
- No playful or gamified elements

Design priorities:
1. Clarity
2. Readability
3. Hierarchy
4. Accessibility

Ads:
- Ads must not interrupt core flows
- Ads are visually separated
- Ads are clearly marked
